{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|戌|火|c1=p|c2=s|t2=fire|ls=psc}}.

''{{w|Shuowen}}'' considers this to be an {{Han compound|戌|火|t1=ninth month|t2=fire|ls=ic|nocap=y}}, probably alluding to a passage in ''{{w|Huainanzi}}'':
: {{zh-x|^火 生 於 寅，壯 於 午，死 於 戌|[The element] fire is born in the first month, is strong in the fifth month, and dies in the ninth month.|CL}}

